      "name": "Kidnap",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>The demon makes an attack against a target of its size or smaller that shares its zone. If successful, instead of dealing damage, the demon grabs the target and lifts it into the air. The target is still able to attack the demon on its turn and can attempt to escape with a TN 6 Exertion check.</p>",
        "action": "full"
      },
